  h2 Who we are
  p Safe to Burn is meant to help homeowners, farmers, and land managers quickly check if weather and environmental conditions are safe for burning brush or debris. By combining local weather data, wind speeds, humidity levels, and official fire alerts, we provide a simple, reliable tool for making responsible burning decisions. Enter your city, state, or ZIP code to see real-time wind speed, humidity, and active burn bans in your area.
